    "description": "LaKeel, Inc. provides product, consulting, and professional services in Japan. The company offers LaKeel DX, a cloud platform that digitizes the enterprise and effectuates strategic IT; LaKeel BI, a self-service business intelligence (BI) tool; and LaKeel Data Insight, an enterprise data management solution. It also provides LaKeel HR, a human resources software; LaKeel online media services for video distribution; LaKeel messenger, a messaging tool; LaKeel eDocument, an electronic books preservation software; LaKeel workflow, a system that allow to build an electronic application and approval system; LaKeel passport, an ID management platform; and LaKeel commerce provides e-commerce solutions. In addition, the company offers LaKeel My Number, an own number for employees and their family members in lump sum; LaKeel Stress Check, a stress check tool for enterprise; LaKeel Survey, an employee survey tools; and LaKeel Process Manager, a business process management platform. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
